Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)グワ～ッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)ナルトが こっちに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,人間業じゃないな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サイ… 何をしている》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,わかった 監視を続けてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,((ナルト : サックラちゃ～ん！))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サクラ : あれが… ナルト…？》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれは…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:57.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,《この草薙の剣をもってしても\N貫けないとはね…》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,《自来也様のおっしゃってた➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,まるで小さな九尾とは\Nこのことか…》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:12.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カブト)これじゃあ\N忍者の戦いというより…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:22.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,まるで\Nバケモノどうしの戦いじゃないか フフッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ナルト…》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:33.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,《大蛇丸 : これ以上 草薙の剣で\Nやり合ってもムダね》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サイ : 状況は どうなってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトは 死んだのか？》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,フフッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:22.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,見なよ… あれを。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:33.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,あんな姿になってまで\Nサスケ君を助けたかったのかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:42.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サスケは絶対 オレが連れて帰る！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:44.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,(一生の約束だってばよ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:50.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サクラちゃん オレ\N約束 絶対 守るってばよ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:54.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,((まっすぐ\N自分の言葉は曲げねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,(それが オレの忍道だからよ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,今じゃ 自分の意識すら\Nとんでしまってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,悲しい子だ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,待て！ サクラ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,今のナルトに近づくんじゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう… もう いいから！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ君は アタシが助け出してみせる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから… ナルトはもう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:46.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,《やばい！》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サイ : 何をするつもりだ？》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ うぅっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,《今がチャンスか…》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:23.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,そろそろ 時間のようね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,《大蛇丸 : やっぱり この体じゃ\N拒絶反応が 出てしまう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:34.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,残念だけど\N遊びは ここまでね…》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,我慢… 我慢よ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:49.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,私には サスケ君が いる…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,あ～あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,《クソッ！ 間に合わなかったか！》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:51.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,ううっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,はぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,手は 出させん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,早とちりだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう キミたちに\N手を 出すつもりはない…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,それどころか その逆さ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:45.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,…どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:03.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクたちと キミたちには\N同じ目的が ある…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,暁が ジャマだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カブト)キミたちを 生かしておけば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:20.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,暁の もう１人くらいは\N始末してくれるかもしれないと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふと 思ってね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ナルト…》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:54.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,《傷の治りが\N思ったよりも 遅い…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:58.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが いつまでも ボランティアを\Nやってるわけにもいかないな…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:06.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,《大蛇丸様も そろそろ時間だ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,助ける代わりに…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,暁を １人でも多く\N始末してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:22.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カブト)といっても\Nあれは キミたちの連れだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:25.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カブト)あとは\Nキミたちで なんとかしなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:32.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,《引き上げどきだな…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,《今しかない！》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:58.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,はぁ… はぁ… はぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:06.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)ボクは ダンゾウ様の使い。\N敵では ありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:10.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,あなたに お話が あります。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,火影式耳順術！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,廓庵入鄽垂手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,はぁ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:08.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐうぅぅ… くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:17.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐぅぅっ… くぅっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:24.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐっ ぐぅあぁぁぁっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダンゾウ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:51.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの もうろくじじい…\Nまだ 生きてたのね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:56.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,で… 話って何かしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:19:00.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダンゾウ様から\N大蛇丸様に伝言があります。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:03.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,実は…。\N(大蛇丸)その前に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:08.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,私への言葉は 慎重に選びなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:15.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,でないと 死ぬわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:19.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボクは ダンゾウ様が\Nおっしゃったとおりにしか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,申しあげられません。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,それで\Nお気に召さぬことがあれば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうぞ ご自由に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐあぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:30.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,里を抜けたサスケに代わり\Nカカシ班に配属された謎の新人 サイ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:34.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,絵心に長け\N忍法 「超獣偽画」により➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:38.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,描いた絵を実体化する能力を持つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:42.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,一切 感情というものがなく\N周囲の空気が読めないため➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:45.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,無神経な発言も多い。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイは 「根」と呼ばれる組織に\N所属している模様。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:55.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,「根」とは 三代目 火影様と\N火影の椅子を巡って争っていた➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:22:00.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,タカ派の主導者 ダンゾウによって\N作られた 暗部養成所のこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:05.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,今日 サイが ダンゾウによる極秘任務を\N受けている可能性も➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,否定できない。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:11.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,でもまぁ ボクの目の黒いうちは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:13.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,思いどおりにはさせないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:52.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto is over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is not human...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sai, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:43.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.\NContinue to observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:00.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's...Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:56.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't pierce through...\N{\i1}even with my snake sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is what Master Jiraiya\N{\i1}was referring to when he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's "like a small Nine-Tailed Beast."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:01.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sakura's Tears\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:12.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not like a Ninja battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:21.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but more like\Na battle between monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:27.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:33.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless to go on fighting\N{\i1}with the snake sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:43.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the situation like?\N{\i1}Is Naruto dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he still wants\Nto save Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,even in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am going to take back Sasuke,\N{\i1}no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my lifelong promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:49.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sakura! I...will keep my promise,\N{\i1}no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:56.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To stand firm with what I say...\N{\i1}That's my Way of the Ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:04.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,By now, even his self-consciousness\Nis gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sad kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get close to Naruto\Nin that state!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:33.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...that's enough!\NI will save Sasuke, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, it's enough...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:45.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now is my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As expected,\N{\i1}this body is rejecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:34.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too bad, but the fun ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:48.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Patience... Patience now...\NI have Sasuke with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:00.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn!\N{\i1}I didn't make it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rushing to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan to fight you guys\N